-------------------------
INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
-------------------------

MailWatch default Apache configuration

- For Apache 2.2:

  Copy the file mailwatch.conf to /etc/apache2/conf.d/

  Reload Apache '/etc/init.d/apache2 reload'

- For Apache 2.4:

  Copy the file mailwatch.conf to /etc/apache2/conf-available/

  Type 'a2enconf mailwatch.conf'

  Reload Apache 'service apache2 reload'

You can also create a d√©dicated whost for MailWatch but don't forgot to remove the config in Apache conf.d.
